    "CONSORT-AI has been referenced by policy and regulatory bodies including the WHO 76, FDA 77 and MHRA 78, and has received over 400 citations to date.",
    "Despite this, we found that there remains low journal uptake, so mechanisms to lower the bar for adoption may require further consideration.",
    "One method to address this could be through editorial systems with tick boxes for authors to indicate the type of work being submitted, where the appropriate reporting checklist could be automatically delivered to be submitted with the paper.",
    "Such mechanisms will help ensure transparent reporting whilst reducing the burden on journal editors.",
    "This systematic review provided an opportunity to assess the applicability and interpretation of CONSORT-AI recommendations across a diverse range of RCTs published since September 2020."
